Commit Message: Initial format_HW.py script: rough draft. Successfully combines multiple kinds of files into PDFs.
Modification that allows text files to be included.
Reorganized into an installable script, including setup.py and an executable script.
Fixed a couple of bugs involving spaces in LaTeX names.

Fixed a bug where PDFs on their own (not concatenated) weren't formatted. Set it up so that it chooses for the PDF the most recent version of each file, in case different files were submitted at different attempts.
Added Rmd and Rnw files (as verbatim)
